title: Homeworld Soundtrack - FLAC version
description:
With the new Homeworld Remastered Collection that came out recently, I figured it was time that the soundtrack (and the original rips from this site) was readdressed. 

In line with some of my other releases, I decided to rip the original CD (I did buy this game years ago and love it as much as when I first bought it; also got this remastered collection) and encode the soundtrack in FLAC. Unfortunately, I was not able to find a FLAC version of YES's song from The Ladder, so I added the version from the Relic Homeworld Community Website.

Enjoy this latest release, and I suggest buying (or at least downloading) the game, please support the original company making these games/soundtracks as always!

- RubiksFaQ
